e mine is very average) would kill me over and over...  which is fine... that's PvP.... but then the multi hour corpse camping would commence.  And corpse camping is legal in PvP now.  Sigh.  Corpse camping for zone control is one thing...  but it's fine to corpse camp someone, a gm won't lift a finger, even if they're doing it for hours just to harass you.  Ok...  I guess I got started on PvP.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
